import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedApi, Message

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    response = await client.chat_stream(
        messages=[
            Message(
                role="user",
                content="content",
            )
        ],
    )
    async for chunk in response.data:
        yield chunk


asyncio.run(main())

import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedApi, Message

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.chat(
        messages=[
            Message(
                role="user",
                content="Hello",
            )
        ],
    )


asyncio.run(main())
